thread.title: Dollar Little Changed After Recent Losses

author: Ira Iosebashvili
title: Dollar Little Changed After Recent Losses
text:
The dollar pared gains Tuesday as investors locked in gains on recent bets against the U.S. currency.
The Wall Street Journal Dollar index, which measures the U.S. currency against a basket of 16 others, was recently unchanged at 84.43, after rising earlier in the session. The gauge hit its lowest closing value since May 2015 on Monday.
